  "text": "EuroPython 2025 in Prague might be over, but there is another Python community event coming soon, the keenly awaited PyCamp CZ Beta!\n📆 September 12–14 2025\n🗺️ Mlýn Třeštice, South Bohemia\n🙌 Unconference format - Participant-driven program \nWe already have some cool content proposals, including Ukulele workshop by Jakub Vysoky, FastAPI introduction by Mia Bajić, or Python Packaging Overview by Miro Hrončok. 👀  \nGet your tickets soon!\n👉 https://lnkd.in/dH7HBiEZ",
